casebody.data:
Rhonda E. HOLDEN
v.
John Alan HOLDEN. No. 195P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 18, 2005. William Diehl, Jr., Charlotte, James W. Lea, III, Wilmington, for Rhonda E. Holden. Benedict J. Del Re', Jr., for John Alan Holden.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 8th day of April 2005 by Plaintiff in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 18th day of August 2005."
